SOLUTION(EV3(<<'EOT')); 
$BR $BBOLD Solution:$EBOLD  We have 
\[f(x) =\sqrt{4x-x^2} = \sqrt{4-(x-2)^2}.\] Hence the domain of the
function is \([0,4]\) and its range is \([0,2]\);
